Net::DNS::Multicast
===================

This module is designed as an extension of the Net::DNS package
(https://metacpan.org/release/Net-DNS).

The module extends Net::DNS to enable mDNS on local network.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the following module and its dependencies:

    Net::DNS 1.41 or later.


